{"sha": "2421470867f198c3aa57e0a7ab0d473aac4cdd38", "node_id": "C_kwDOANBUbNoAKDI0MjE0NzA4NjdmMTk4YzNhYTU3ZTBhN2FiMGQ0NzNhYWM0Y2RkMzg", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Iain Sandoe", "email": "iain@sandoe.co.uk", "date": "2022-12-22T19:00:13Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Iain Sandoe", "email": "iain@sandoe.co.uk", "date": "2023-01-05T12:48:00Z"}, "message": "modula-2, driver: Handle static-libstd++ for targets without static/dynamic\n\nThe follows the pattern used in C++ and D drivers to pass -static-libstdc++\nonto the target driver to allow spec substitution of static libraries.\n\nNOTE: The handling of Bstatic/dynamic and the possible use of static libgm2\nlibraries is unimplemented in this driver so far.\n\nSigned-off-by: Iain Sandoe <iain@sandoe.co.uk>\n\ngcc/m2/ChangeLog:\n\n\t* gm2spec.cc (lang_specific_driver): Pass -static-libstdc++ on to\n\tthe target driver if the linker does not support Bstatic/dynamic.", "tree": {"sha": "e21c9b07cd8f016e3502163316a448d76f6e4b74", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/trees/e21c9b07cd8f016e3502163316a448d76f6e4b74"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/commits/2421470867f198c3aa57e0a7ab0d473aac4cdd38", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/2421470867f198c3aa57e0a7ab0d473aac4cdd38", "html_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commit/2421470867f198c3aa57e0a7ab0d473aac4cdd38", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/2421470867f198c3aa57e0a7ab0d473aac4cdd38/comments", "author": {"login": "iains", "id": 4039407, "node_id": "MDQ6VXNlcjQwMzk0MDc=", "avatar_url": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4039407?v=4", "gravatar_id": "", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/iains", "html_url": "https://github.com/iains", "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/iains/followers", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/